\v 1 Sondelani, zizwe, ukuze lizwe\x + Hlab. 49.1.\x*; lani bantu, lilalele; umhlaba kawuzwe\x + 1.2. Dute. 32.1.\x*, lokugcwala kwawo; ilizwe, lakho konke okuvela kilo\x + 42.5. Jobe 31.8. Jobe 5.25.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba intukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* iphezu kwazo zonke izizwe, lolaka phezu kwawo wonke amabutho azo; izitshabalalisile\x + 34.2.\x*, izinikele ekubulaweni.
